                            The flexible, fast, and secure template language for PHP
                        </dd>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative">
                        <dt>
                            <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-green-500 text-white">
                                <!-- Heroicon name: outline/annotation -->
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 13h6m-3-3v6m5 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">FlySystem</p>
