                            </div>
                            <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Codeception</p>
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
                            Codeception collects and shares best practices and solutions for testing PHP web applications
                        </dd>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative">
                        <dt>
                            <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-green-500 text-white">
                                <!-- Heroicon name: outline/annotation -->
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
