                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">OAuth 2.0 Server</p>
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">
                            A standards compliant implementation of an OAuth 2.0 authorization server written in PHP which makes working with OAuth 2.0 trivial.
                        </dd>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative">
                        <dt>
                            <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center h-12 w-12 rounded-md bg-green-500 text-white">
                                <!-- Heroicon name: outline/annotation -->
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="ml-16 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Symfony Console</p>
